features.name: text
nominal_values: a stupid and incompetent movie that doesnt even have the benefit of being trashily enjoyable .
it tries to make us swallow things that a better movie would be stopped cold by or just plain omit entirely .
its a waste of wesley snipes and woody harrelson who are enjoyable actors in their own rights but are nauseating here .
its not even fun as trash .
its not simply idiotic its contemptuous of its audience .
money train is one of the worst movies i have ever seen .
weslely and woody would do well to leave this off their resumes .
